1. How to install Java Runtime environment:
	- Go to http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/index.html
	- Click on download button below "JRE".
	- Click "accept the license agreement"
	- Click on the link corresponding to Windows x86 Offline/Windows x64 depending on whether
	  your machine is 64 bit or 32 bit.
	- Download the file and install JRE.
	
2. Installing Apache Tomcat Server
	- Go to http://tomcat.apache.org/download-80.cgi
	- On left side click on 32-bit/64-bit Windows Service Installer
